Description_lang: N'Zoth selects pairs of players and fills their minds with all-consuming Paranoia for $316541d. Paranoid players must be within $316676A1 yards of their paired partner or suffer $309978s1 Shadow damage every $316541s1 sec. This damage increases over the duration of Paranoia.Affected players do not trust their allies while paranoid. Coming within $316676A1 yards of an unpaired ally causes the player with Paranoia to be drained of $s1 sanity every $316541s1 sec while they remain near their ally.
